room_title: Escape room "The Heist" by The Great Escape Clovis in Fresno
room_description: All you need to do is steal the Cora Sun-drop Diamond on display in this art gallery and you would never have to work again. You will be going in as a team of criminals and your job will be to work together to conquer the puzzles, solve the riddles and navigate the laser maze in order to steal the famous Cora Sun-drop Diamond without setting off the alarms and spending the rest of your lives in prison.
